# Repair

Diagnose and fix workspace state inconsistencies.

## Invocation
```bash
slipway repair
```

## Contract
- Scans workspace state for orphaned files, stale locks, and corrupt records.
- Applies deterministic fixes where possible.
- Reports what was found and fixed.
- Show repair summary to user.

## Flags
- `--json`: JSON output (separates applied repairs from unrepaired drift)
- `--focus <alias>`: repair focus alias — repair currently exposes no public focuses (default local-integrity route only)
- `--list-focuses`: list public repair focuses (currently none)
- `--format <text|json>`: output format for `--list-focuses`
{{- end -}}
